channel.title: Autospawn.cfg error 317 [HELP]
channel.description:
//------NpcID---CoordX--CoordY--Height--RangeX1-RangeY1-RangeX2-RangeY2-WalkType-Descrption spawn = 540 3224 3219 0 0 0 0 0 2 Weapon_Trader
spawn = 873 3225 3219 0 0 0 0 0 2 Armor_Trader [ENDOFSPAWN]
Well the first one worked fine but the second one says in the Console: Your Server Is Now Up..... Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "3 219 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1814) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:23) at server.main(server.java:28)
Any one know why it's telling me that?
